XML-Simple: XML-Simple (XML::Simple Perl XML Module)
XML-Simple: 
XML-Simple: XML::Simple is a Perl module that was originally developed as a tool 
XML-Simple: for reading and writing configuration data in XML format. You can use 
XML-Simple: it for many other purposes that involve storing and retrieving 
XML-Simple: structured data in XML.
XML-Simple: 
XML-Simple: XML-Simple was written by Grant McLean.
